org.apache.streams.data

Interface ActivityObjectConverter<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable

    public interface ActivityObjectConverter<T>
extends Serializable
    Converts non-ActivityObject documents to ActivityObjects and back.

    Each converter may return zero or one alternative representations.
